<p class="">Is not that evidence that the United States are convinced that Japan is constructing 16-inch guns?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f3c53826-4710-4e8d-8109-265070c5c01a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
