            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-43956212-8d28-4994-bb89-b2946c3b2238" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-20/debates/2ccc3e41-2d72-48bd-8bfc-34c8c1a4f814/LondonNavalTreatyBill#contribution-43956212-8d28-4994-bb89-b2946c3b2238">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
